import React, { useState } from 'react';
import * as S from './ExpenseForm.style';

const ExpenseForm = () => {

    return (
        <S.MainWrapper>
        <S.Form>
            <S.Main>
            <S.InputWrapper>
            <S.Label>Title</S.Label>
            <S.FormInput type='text' />
            </S.InputWrapper>
            <S.InputWrapper>
            <S.Label>Amount</S.Label>
            <S.FormInput type='number' />
            </S.InputWrapper>
            </S.Main>
            <S.Main>
            <S.InputWrapper>
            <S.Label>Date</S.Label>
            <S.FormInput type='date' />
            </S.InputWrapper>
            </S.Main>
            <S.ButtonWrapper>
            <S.Button type='submit'>Add Expense</S.Button>
            </S.ButtonWrapper>
        </S.Form>
        </S.MainWrapper>
    );
}

export default ExpenseForm;
